<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-08-0478 </DOCNO><TEXT>The aim of the project was to study the problems of frost heave due tofreezing around earth heat pipes and especially the risk of these pipeswandering upwards. Calculations and tests show that the type of accumulatedheave may occur and that it is possible to estimate the risk from theproperties of the ground and the pipe temperature.</TEXT></DOC>